ated as the total K10 distress score for each participant: 10-19 = no psychological distress, 20-24 = mild psychological distress, 25-29 = moderate psychological distress, and 30-50 = severe  psychological distress. 5. Use multinomial logistic regression to examine associations between psychological distress severity and gender and motivation for distance learning (reference category: no distress.",
